These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, azure, aquamarine, blue
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, turkish, french, german
4 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, monopoly, snooker
4 different pets are kept: rat, pony, hamster, hedgehog
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, dunhill, vegafina, aristoff
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, broccoli, garlic, pepper
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, december, october, april
 1. the person who likes ivory is the owner of the rat##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the dutch##1
 3. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 4. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing canasta is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who likes azure##1
 7. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the french##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is the dunhill-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
11. the person eating cucumber is the person who likes azure##1
12. the person who's birthday is in december is the vegafina-smoker##1
13. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
14. the person eating broccoli is the person who likes blue##1
15. the person eating pepper is the person playing monopoly##1
16. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
17. the person who likes aquamarine is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4      |
| Color      | ivory       | blue      | aquamarine       | azure    |
| Nationality         | dutch    | german    | turkish      | french    |
| Game           | snooker | backgammon       | monopoly | canasta     |
| Pet   | rat         | hamster  | hedgehog      | pony     |
| Cigar   | dunhill          | aristoff     | vegafina       | havana |
| Food         | garlic       | broccoli | pepper       | cucumber   |
| Birthday     | april     | october  | december         | february   |

