.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, oliveros, bluemaster, bolivar
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, october, september, february
City: venice, hamburg, paris, colone
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, skiing, cycling, tennis
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, pink, grey, brown
4 different games are played: chess, billiard, whist, poker
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, balloon-flower, rose, tulip
 1. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 2. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 8. the person traveling to paris is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 9. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
11. the person playing whist is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
12. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
13. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
14. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person playing chess##1
15. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
16. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
17. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3      |      4      |
| Cigar          | bluemaster     | oliveros     | havana      | bolivar  |
| Birthday         | february  | august  | september      | october |
| City   | colone   | paris     | venice | hamburg        |
| Sport   | soccer    | skiing        | cycling        | tennis        |
| Color   | grey | lilac | brown   | pink  |
| Game           | poker   | chess       | billiard        | whist       |
| Flower     | amaryllis     | rose     | tulip       | balloon-flower     |

