.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-3::.
City: marseilles, venice, prague, hamburg
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, game, fonseca, cain
4 different games are played: canasta, poker, bridge, monopoly
There are 4 different nationalities: british, french, brazilian, indian
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, roller
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, almond-milk, sprite
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, february, january
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
 3. the person driving the jet-ski is the person traveling to venice##1
 4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the french##1
 7. the brazilian is on the left of the indian##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking sprite is the french##1
11. the person playing poker is the person traveling to marseilles##1
12. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the indian is on the left of the french##1
14. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
15. the game-smoker is the person driving the roller##1
16. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
17. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |     3     |      4      |
| City          | prague          | hamburg        | venice      | marseilles      |
| Cigar         | cain       | fonseca       | swisher    | game |
