There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, baccarat, game, alhambra
 1. the person who likes purple is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person eating dunhillrot##1
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the alhambra-smoker##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is the game-smoker##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
12. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person drinking water##1
13. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
14. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
15. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
16. the person eating dunhillrot is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

